openMotif ( X libraries)

Open Motif is the freely available source code
distribution for the Motif user interface component 
toolkit. Open Motif is built on top of the standard
X Toolkit(Xt) and X11 libraries.


** DEPENDENCIES **
xlt (libXlt libraries), this SlackBuild is currently available 
  on http://batts.mine.nu/pub/src/SlackBuilds/xlt/, and should 
  be on http://www.slackbuilds.org/ at some point.
